== Geography ==
Bari is the largest urban and metro area on the [[Adriatic Sea|Adriatic]].  It is located in [[Southern Italy]], at a more northerly latitude than [[Naples]], further south than [[Rome]].

=== Climate ===
Bari has a [[Mediterranean climate]] ([[Köppen climate classification|Köppen]]: ''Csa'') with mild winters and hot, dry summers.
